Based on the detailed structure of your current scripts and the orchestration logic found in `run_analysis.sh`, here is an updated `README.md`. This version enhances the documentation of the directory structure, clarifies the multi-track processing (Unaligned vs. Bracken), and adds a "Quick Start" section for the pipeline.

